00:00:11,845 --> 00:00:13,555
Glupan!

4
00:00:26,276 --> 00:00:27,277
Nada.

5
00:00:37,370 --> 00:00:39,122
Epizoda prva.

6
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:46,671
Biti u pećnici, estar
